    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/5ff759f6ff4d608a348592f9b5fdc01c.avif?t=1762882607\" width=610 height=198 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Daemonium》是一款支持1至4人在线合作的心理恐怖游戏。恶魔附身正在蔓延。拿起你的装备，与队友一起寻找恶魔存在的源头。进入恶魔领域，阻止附身。执行驱魔仪式，在它夺走你的灵魂之前将其逐回地狱。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>- “有史以来最令人印象深刻的驱魔仪式之一”</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/1f8e7b92daf23d1144ba47a3611e141c.avif?t=1762882607\" width=487 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可以在各种场景中游戏，每局还会随机生成恶魔领域</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/ba9ebcdf7becdccc7c51104346d822e2.poster.avif?t=1762882607\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/ba9ebcdf7becdccc7c51104346d822e2.webm?t=1762882607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/ba9ebcdf7becdccc7c51104346d822e2.mp4?t=1762882607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/e780ad9b3595fd1a1f5332f006195061.avif?t=1762882607\" width=487 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持最多4人合作游玩</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/858fb28fafa560486e92ce1a3809b876.poster.avif?t=1762882607\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/858fb28fafa560486e92ce1a3809b876.webm?t=1762882607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/858fb28fafa560486e92ce1a3809b876.mp4?t=1762882607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/1cf7108bec0125e38baa34fcf6dacd11.avif?t=1762882607\" width=487 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用各种设备寻找超自然现象的证据，并揭示被附身的物品</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/8adf631dbf701eb79ab38d7431693d99.poster.avif?t=1762882607\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/8adf631dbf701eb79ab38d7431693d99.webm?t=1762882607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/8adf631dbf701eb79ab38d7431693d99.mp4?t=1762882607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/1c57e731e6e41637ed9b62cda8eaaf47.avif?t=1762882607\" width=503 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >清除被附身的物品</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/fa91e8eefba1dbbf6dc698b2cc3e9510.poster.avif?t=1762882607\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/fa91e8eefba1dbbf6dc698b2cc3e9510.webm?t=1762882607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/fa91e8eefba1dbbf6dc698b2cc3e9510.mp4?t=1762882607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/b2b62fcd8c22ebbf7c760c8e42025229.avif?t=1762882607\" width=552 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冒险进入恶魔领域</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/d08711b462f85acd734db0cf62301266.poster.avif?t=1762882607\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/d08711b462f85acd734db0cf62301266.webm?t=1762882607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/d08711b462f85acd734db0cf62301266.mp4?t=1762882607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/f53d7ab21e78e92c8b541e1b5096b004.avif?t=1762882607\" width=552 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在恶魔领域执行驱魔仪式，将恶魔放逐回地狱</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/0236687527e018980bc6888fd6cfc176.poster.avif?t=1762882607\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/0236687527e018980bc6888fd6cfc176.webm?t=1762882607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/0236687527e018980bc6888fd6cfc176.mp4?t=1762882607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
